**Overview**

This dashboard is an overview of the different threat intelligence indicators with a **threat.indicator.type: file**.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of your indicators like hash type counters, popular domains, statistics about how many unique indicators are ingested and other relevant information. The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of the ingestion of indicators from Cybersixgill. The dashboard only shows the active indicators that are not expired. The indicators are expired after the duration set by `IOC Expiration Duration` in the integration settings since the time they are created(`@timestamp`).
